{"tid":103764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[發泄]大家有冇見過幸運的肥芝？","createTime":"2017-02-01T14:42:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-27T15:07:31.000Z","uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"390f943fbe92c7166ffae2c8786651701b68514a","tid":103764,"uid":66252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"有種肥芝係比較幸運的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地有齊所有肥芝格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n包括任性霸道港女 當所有野都係奉旨<br />\n周圍同人講邊個邊個中意佢 但其實係會錯意<br />\n然而 幸運既佢地 冇肥芝既身形 有部分甚至係靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以佢地成為左瘦芝 恰巧我身邊就有一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本我當佢係fd 但愈深入了解佢就愈覺得辛苦<br />\n例如佢叫我幫佢既語氣係命令式 &quot;我要依個&quot;<br />\n洗人唔洗本既公主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來我成日揾佢 佢都藍剔 我就冇再揾佢<br />\n近來佢sd左個msg黎 話佢男神好似中意左我<br />\n<br />\n我只想說一句<br />\n關我撚事啊八婆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時又唔見你會覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵你到依家都冇男朋友 拍親拖都係散拖啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe1055942734327d9a70a356de067b007cd65eb","tid":103764,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T16:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1009aa5572c465c55142de630d16ee3bc68e26e5","tid":103764,"uid":64002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:42:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好悶呀 最近無得睇你狙擊肥婆post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e1516c02a2e5953ad9ae88765b86af78f8a649